data: Kemono Friends is a multimedia franchise created by Mine Yoshizaki, creator of Sgt. Frog. It takes place in a massive zoo where all of the animals have mutated into girls because some volcano erupted glitter. There are 3           and there have been 7 official games, with 2 of them actually having a story. There are also have been three stage plays as well as a few live performances of the many in-universe idol songs./n/nAlso, manga.
